g.text: This workflow, the deployment workflow, reads the trained model, as well as the new transaction and applies the model to classify
it. Like in the training workflow we use a Rule Engine node to apply the custom threshold. In case a transaction is classified as
fraudulent the workflow sends an email to the fraud department.
